msgstr ""
"However, [a slightly modified version of "
"Pandoc](https://github.com/yanntrividic/pandoc/) was developed to support"
" reading paragraph and character styles. To use it, you must [compile it "
"from "
"source](https://github.com/yanntrividic/pandoc/blob/main/INSTALL.md)."

#: ../../source/md/2_installation.md:69
