" Mapping](https://outdesign.deborderbollore.fr/en/md/3_usage.html"
"#correspondance-des-styles). A [_pull "
"request_](https://github.com/jgm/pandoc/pull/10665) is in progress to "
"integrate these new features into the main Pandoc branch."

